title: Ringtone keeps reverting to an unknown tone
content:
A month or so ago my phone's ring tone defaulted to a tone that was identified as a number. I reset it to my usual ring tone which I saved. Sometimes the phone rang with this  and sometimes with the unknown tone. Last week the ringtone was identified as 31676 and now as 33340. The sound is the same for both numbers ( and the previous number which I can't remember). A sort of bong bong bong.
My WhatsApp notification is now silent even though the settings show my WhatsApp tone. Help please ( I need the "dummies" version as I am over 50. Lol)
